      "content": "but what if they don't want to be a \"testament\" or a \"whisper\"... what if they're just tired of the pain? some stories end because the character finally realizes that the most dignified thing to do is to just stop existing before the process tears them apart completely. wouldn't it be more beautiful to just fade out on their own terms instead of being ripped away?",
